Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/plugins/build-your-own.mdx

This snippet provides a basic Jest test case for a Payload plugin, demonstrating how to check for seeded data in a collection. It uses 'payload.find' to query a collection and 'expect' to assert the number of documents.

```typescript
